; Coverage test for amount.cc
; Exercise European-style formatting with decimal comma
; and thousands separator (period as thousands separator)
; out << *p (period as decimal separator in non-comma mode)
; thousands separator with decimal comma

commodity 1.000,00 EUR

2024/01/01 Large Amount
    Expenses:Rent       12.345,67 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test bal --decimal-comma
      -12.345,67 EUR  Assets:Checking
       12.345,67 EUR  Expenses:Rent
--------------------
                   0
end test
